{
  "texts": [
    "This work is a combination of dense blocks with skip connections for decreasing the number of parameters necessary for the model with the same accuracy.",
    "The CondenseNets is having significantly fewer parameters than other deep CNNs and also gives the better results for image classification.The purpose Multi-Scale Dense Networks (MSDNet) architecture is to attain more computationally efficient than other deep CNNs [15].",
    "The architecture uses a mixture of dense blocks with various growth rates and it helps to enable multi-scale feature learning.",
    "The MSDNet is also more suitable e Image classification.",
    "The CNN architecture based on the reinforcement learning which is automatically searching for neural network parameter is proposed in [16]."
  ]
}